data.description: POOL and very desirable neighborhood.  This 3 bedroom 2 bath home offers a large kitchen with a cozy dining nook, breakfast bar plus a full separate dining room.  The family room has vaulted ceilings and a pellet fireplace for those cooler days ahead.  Relax in the spacious master bedroom with walk-in closet, double sink vanity, separate shower and large jetted tub.  The back patio runs the full length of the home giving you plenty of space to enjoy your beautiful pool.  I can not imagine wanting to leave this little oasis, but if you do have an RV, there is space on site to store it at home.  Once you step inside you will understand why this house transcends into a home.  Solar lien to be assumed by Buyer~  Back on the market, Buyer unable to proceed.
